mahakavi kalidasu ( english : mahakavi of mahakavi ) is a 1960 telugu , drama film , produced by p. adinarayana rao on &lt;unk&gt; productions banner and directed by &lt;unk&gt; nageswara rao . starring akkineni nageswara rao , savitri in the lead roles and music composed by pendyala nageswara rao .